{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "聂方标护送受伤的潇湘堡主及其女萧凌南下，途经保定赶上\"打春\"仪式。萧凌触景生情，思念古浊飘。人群中出现一名青衣少年，身手不凡，在萧凌险些跌倒时出手相救。展一帆追至，欲与青衣少年动手，却误与聂方标交手。四川唐门笑面追魂唐化龙赶到劝和，引见双方。青衣少年嬉笑间扬长而去。聂方标透露潇湘堡主遭残金毒掌所伤，古浊飘疑为魔头传人。唐化龙、展一帆等转赴北京，于平安镖局与孙清羽、林佩奇会合，商议对付残金毒掌。众人以拜访为名前往相国府见古浊飘，古浊飘机智应对，约众人子夜在郊外废宅相见。古浊飘命棋儿去卷帘子胡同通知其独臂爷爷晚间来见。棋儿至爷爷处，老人感念古浊飘救命之恩（当年古浊飘曾救祖孙二人性命并替其报仇），决心自断拇指中指以报恩。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_ba_shi",
      "speaker_name": "车把式",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "客官，你老鸿运高照，刚好可以赶到保定去看'打春'。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_che_ba_shi",
      "text": "今天已经是立春了，日子过得倒真快。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_ba_shi",
      "speaker_name": "车把式",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "可不是日子过得快，去年小的也是在保定府看的打春，喝，那可真热闹得紧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_ba_shi",
      "speaker_name": "车把式",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "好教你老知道，小的这辆车赶的路子，正是往保定东门那儿走，现在还没有过戌时，城东琼花观里，可正热闹咧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "萧凌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "又下雪啦。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "今天刚好赶上打春，前面人拥挤得很，车子看样子是走不通了，姑娘如果觉得好了些的话，何不出来看看，也散散心。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_ba_shi",
      "speaker_name": "车把式",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "您站到这车座上面来，才看得清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_che_ba_shi",
      "speaker_name": "车把式",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "你老也上去看看，那纸扎的春牛和芒神可大的咧！站在檐下面穿着吉服的就是保定府的大老爷，现在还唱着戏文哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ling",
      "speaker_name": "萧凌",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "这人怎么这样糊涂，人家在做戏，又不是真的，他发什么威？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "想不到在这些人里，还有武林高手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "像姑娘这么俏生生的人儿，怎么能到这种地方，等会儿摔坏了身子，多不好。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少年",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "尊驾也要小心些，跌坏了身子可不是玩的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "朋友，招子放亮些，这里可不是你逞口舌之快的地方。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "好朋友，这才叫天下无处不逢君，想不到山不转路转，竟又让我们在这里碰上了，真教我姓展的高兴得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "闪开些！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "你干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "好朋友果然有两下子！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少年",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ling",
      "text": "那人本是冲着小可来的，想不到却和尊友动上了手。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "展老弟，怎的在这里动起手来！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "展老弟，快些住手，都是自己人。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "保定府尹就在这里，等下惊动了官面上的人，那可就有些麻烦了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "text": "原来是唐大侠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "一别经年，聂兄怎的也到此地来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "是否带着宝眷到京城去过年的，那正好和兄弟同路。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "你们俩怎会动上手的？来来，我给你们两位引见引见，这位就是江湖上鼎鼎大名的入云神龙聂少侠，展老弟想必也听过这名头吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "这位展一帆，展少侠，虽然初出道，却是当今点苍掌门人的高弟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们两位都是名门正派掌门人的高弟，以后可得多亲近亲近。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "聂大侠为什么不将尊友也替我们引见一下。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "我们路上多承尊友一路照顾，还未曾谢过哩。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小生一介书生，可高攀不上聂大侠这种朋友。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天气这么冷，小生在这里实在呆不住了，如果大侠们没有什么吩咐的话，就此告辞。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "text": "朋友，真人不露眼，但我姓唐的自问眼睛不瞎，还看得出阁下是高人来，不过在下们与阁下既无新仇，更无宿怨，朋友屡次相戏，却有些说不过去了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "青衣少年",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "text": "阁下可别弄错了，小可只是一介书生，可不是什么高人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是唐大哥拦住小弟，小弟倒要看看他究竟是什么变的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "展老弟，你又何苦无端生这些闲气？人家也没有怎的，多一事不如少一事，何况你不是还要赶到京城去斗一斗残金毒掌吗？",
      "tone": "劝解",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "展大侠若能为武林除此魔头，实是我等之幸——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "聂兄远来河朔，大概也是为着和兄弟同一原因吧？听说潇湘堡中，此次居然也有人来，终南一剑郁达夫也在河朔一带现过行踪，北京城里，想必是热闹得很了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "舍弟们一听京城中群贤毕集，就等不及似的拉着我出来，刚好展老弟也恰好在舍间，闻言也和兄弟一齐来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "想不到在这里又遇见聂兄，真是好极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "兄弟在家里闷了多年，想不到一出来就遇着如此热闹的场面。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "text": "小弟此刻却不是上北京城去的，而是刚从北京城里出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "text": "不瞒唐兄，此刻坐在车子里的，就是潇湘堡主萧大侠和玉剑萧姑娘父女两人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "text": "原来萧老前辈也在这里，不知聂兄能否替我们引见一下。",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小可虽远在滇南，但对潇湘堡主的侠名，早巳心仪，想不到今日有幸能在这里遇着他老前辈的侠驾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位道路之上难道没有听说潇湘堡主已在京畿遭了残金毒掌的毒手了吗？兄弟此次离京南下，为的就是护送萧老前辈回堡疗伤。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事说来话长，各位到了京城，可到铁指金丸韦老前辈处，天灵星孙老前辈和龙舌剑林大侠也全都在那里，各位见着他们，就可以知道此事的详情了，唉——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总之，今日江湖已满伏危机，最可怕的是，那残金毒掌似乎已有了传人，而他的传人竟是当今的相国公子。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟此刻待命在身，不得不远离京畿，但望各位到了京城后，能有一个对付残金毒掌的有效办法！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nie_fang_biao",
      "speaker_name": "聂方标",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "尤其是那位古公子，以堂堂相国公子的身份，却做了武林魔头的爪牙，此人若不除去，只怕武林中不知有多少的鲜血要染在他身上了，兄弟此次事情一了，也得立刻赶回京城，但愿兄弟还能赶得上各位除去这武林败类的盛举。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这姓古的在北京城里安稳了几天，不好受的日子也该到了。",
      "tone": "自负",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "公子现在正在后园，请您从侧门过去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "speaker_name": "林佩奇",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "那么便麻烦少管家引路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_lin_pei_qi",
      "text": "我家公子说，和您同来的爷台们也请和您做一处去，公子这两天身子不大舒服，是以没有亲自出来接您，还请您原谅则个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "你老也来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 409,
      "line_end": 409
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位小心些！",
      "tone": "提醒",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天气阴湿，路上又滑，别跌倒了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 433,
      "line_end": 433
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "小可冒昧，阁下想必就是古公子了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 441,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "小可久闻大名，今日得见，果然名不虚传。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 445,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "text": "阁下想必就是展一帆展大侠了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 451,
      "line_end": 451
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_yu",
      "text": "这位大概就是四川唐门中的侠士，我古浊飘何德何能，竟致劳动各位的大驾，实在惶恐得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_yu",
      "speaker_name": "唐化羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "小可与公子素昧平生，公子怎——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小可无状，言词草率，再加上各位上次临行之际，小可都没有恭送，心里一直遗憾得很，却想不到各位宽宏大量，此刻又枉驾敝处，小可高兴之余，特此当面谢过，还请恕罪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 471,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "小可们江湖草民，打扰公子多次，已是不当，再加上伤病之人，更不敢在相府中打扰，公子明人，想必知道小可们的苦衷。",
      "tone": "谦恭",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "text": "那么孙老英雄此次枉驾敝处，却是又有何事见教？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 481,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "化龙此次北来，一路上就听说京城中出了位翩翩浊世的佳公子，无论文武两途，都是高人一等，是以化龙入了京城，就不嫌冒昧，借着孙老前辈的引见，来拜会拜会高人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 487,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "text": "唐大侠过誉了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "text": "唐大侠这镖囊中所存的，想必就是名震天下的唐门绝器了，小可久闻玄妙，却始终无缘见识，等会儿一定要拜见一下。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tang_hua_long",
      "speaker_name": "唐化龙",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "雕虫小技，怎人得了方家法眼！等下公子若有兴趣，小可一定将这些不成材的东西拿出来，让公子一一过目一下。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 497,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "古公子人中龙凤，卓俊超人，我等愚昧，有几件事想请教一下。",
      "tone": "谦恭",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 509,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "众位大驾前来，小可本应略尽地上之谊，但不巧得很，家严刚刚差人来着小可前去有事训示，小可不得不暂且失陪，还请各位恕罪。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 513,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位如果有事见教的话，再过半个对时，小可再来就教，只要告诉小可一个地方，自会前来，也用不着再劳动各位的大驾了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_qing_yu",
      "speaker_name": "孙清羽",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子既然有事，小可等自应告退——",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子既然约定夜间见面，那再好也没有，只是我等初来此地，京城里有什么佳处可供清谈的，也不知道，还是公子说定一个地方好了，子正之际，小可们一定去向公子剪烛长谈一番。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 533
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子，我倒想起一个好地方来了，就是那天您去游春时，遇见程大侠的那地方，又清静，又没人，这会小的先差人去打扫一下，摆上一桌酒，在那里无论谈什么，不是都方便得很吗？",
      "tone": "俏皮",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 535,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "棋儿，你不要多口。",
      "tone": "低声",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 539,
      "line_end": 539
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位小管家年纪轻轻，就如此能干，好极了，好极了，这地方再好没有了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 541,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_yi_fan",
      "speaker_name": "展一帆",
      "listener": "char_cheng_gai",
      "text": "等会就有劳程老前辈引路了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 545,
      "line_end": 545
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然展大侠意下如此，就这样决定好了，此刻小可先行告退，失礼之处，恕罪恕罪。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 547,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "公子，我知道您的心情一定苦闷得很，但是再这样下去，您怎么办呢？我——",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 565,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "text": "我身受您的救命之恩，这些年来，一直跟着您，您不但待我好，什么事也没将我当外人看，我年纪虽然小，还不懂得事，但天天看着公子这么苦恼，心里也难受得很。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 569,
      "line_end": 571
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gu_zhuo_piao",
      "speaker_name": "古浊飘",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "你到卷帘子胡同去通知你爷爷一声，叫他吃过晚饭后，到我这里来一趟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 573,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "原来是你，快进来，外面冷得很。",
      "tone": "慈祥",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "你怎么好久没有来看你爷爷了，这儿天气冷，你可要小心呀！别受了凉，唉——",
      "tone": "慈祥",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 599,
      "line_end": 601
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "你要知道，我们夏家就只靠你传宗接代了——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 603,
      "line_end": 603
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "公子呢？这些日子来可好？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 605
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "text": "爷爷，公子叫我来告诉你老人家一声，说是今天晚上请您老人家到他那里去一趟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 611,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好了，好了，我老头子总算有了替公子效力的机会，那么，纵然我死了也可以瞑目了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 615,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "孩子，你可不要忘记，我们两人这条命，都是公子救回来的，若没有公子，不但我们这一老一少早就骨头都凉透了，你爹爹、你妈妈的大仇，又叫谁替我们报去？唉，爷爷现在想起来，那一天的事还好像就在眼前。",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 619,
      "line_end": 621
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "孩子，你真要好好地用功，公子那一身功夫你只要学上一成，就可终生受用不尽了，我们的仇人虽已被公子杀了，仇也替我们报了，但爷爷总想你将来能强爷胜祖，在武林中替姓夏的露露脸。",
      "tone": "慈祥",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 623,
      "line_end": 625
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "孩子，你也跟着来吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 657,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "孩子，你把墙上挂着的那把刀拿下来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 661,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "快把爷爷的大拇指和中指削下来。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 669,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "你听到没有，爷爷的话你敢不听吗？",
      "tone": "严厉",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 673,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "孩子，我问你，这些日子来，你一直跟着公子，他可好吗？",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 677,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "text": "公子这些日子来，总是成天叹着气，脾气也更坏了，一会儿发脾气，一会儿又微笑着，抬头望着天，想着心事。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 683,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_er",
      "speaker_name": "棋儿",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "text": "公子的心里烦，棋儿也知道，可是爷爷……爷爷你……",
      "tone": "哽咽",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 687,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "我们一家身受公子的大恩，怎么报得清！",
      "tone": "感慨",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 689,
      "line_end": 689
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "大丈夫立身于世，讲究的是恩怨分明，有仇不报，固然不好，但身受人家的大恩而不报，也就是个小人了，孩子，你愿不愿意你爷爷做个小人呢？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 691,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂老人",
      "listener": "char_qi_er",
      "text": "那么，孩子，听爷爷的话。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 8,
      "line_start": 695,
      "line_end": 695
    }
  ],
